mod+return start terminal
mod+shift+q kill window
mod+d run dmenu
mod+[jkl;] focus direction
mod+[arrow_keys] focus direction
mod+shift+[jkl;] move direction
mod+shift+[arrow keys] move direction
mod+h split horizontally
mod+v split vertically
mod+f toggle fullscreen
mod+[swe] change layout
mod+shift+space toggle floating
mod+space toggle focus between floating and nonfloating
mod+a focus parent
mod+[number] go to workspace
mod+shift+[number] move to workspace
mod+shift+c reload
mod+shift+r restart
mod+shift+e exit
mod+shift+i start firefox
mod+shift+ctrl+i start firefox in incognito mode
mod+shift+s start steam
volume button change volume 10%
ctrl+volume button change volume 1%
shift+volume button change volume 50%
mute toggle volume
mod+t toggle split orientation
mod+shift+h lock
print screenshot to ~/tmp/out.png
mod+shift+t move workspace to right screen
mod+r resize mode
mod+c mouse mode
mod+m screen mode
mod+n wallpaper mode
mod+shift+v volume mode
mod+shift+p play the clipboard with tts
mod+shift+f fakebusy
mod+shift+ctrl+n timer now
mod+shift+return start terminal and change toggle orientation
mod+shift+ctrl+k calculator dropdown
mod+shift+ctrl+t time dropdown
mod+shift+ctrl+v vim dropdown
mod+shift+ctrl+p pavucontrol
